Flex's mobile app helps you manage your practice from wherever you are — all your patient text messages and full Open Dental schedule are just a tap away.

Key features include:

Patient Communication
>> Two-way text messaging fully synced with Flex in your office & Open Dental comms log
>> Fast patient search with quick-access info like date of birth, family members, balance due and next appointment time

Mobile Appointment Book
>> View your always up-to-date schedule across in any operatory
>> Add new patients to Open Dental
>> Manage your schedule: View key details and create & edit appointments

Flexible & Secure
>> Support for multi-location practices built right in
>> Fully HIPAA-compliant
>> Administrators can add, limit or remove staff access instantly from inside Flex
>> Two-factor verification required
